---
title: Sweet and Sour Beef with Mange Tout, Red Peppers and Egg Noodles
description: Scrap the takeaway plans and opt for the real deal with tonight’s mouthwateringly delicious sweet and sour beef. Full on flavour on the table in 30 minutes. What are you waiting for? Crunchy veggies, juicy beef, noodles and a glossy sweet and sour sauce to boot, this dish is bursting with ingredients you can’t help but love.
